paragraphs.context: With a fleet of autonomous Jaguar I-Pace vehicles, Wayve plans to expand beyond London as it has tested its technology in five other cities in the UK. Artificial intelligence expert Amar Shah founded the company alongside Alex Kendal in London in 2017. Shah led the firm as its CEO until 2020.
